OL,3,CWhat happens next in the election of a
OL,4,Cnew First Minister in Wales?
OL,6,FOnce Welsh Labour has elected a new
OL,7,Fleader on Saturday, attention turns to
OL,8,Fthe Senedd for subsequent events.JMark
OL,9,FDrakeford will no longer be leader of
OL,10,FWelsh Labour but he will remain First
OL,11,FMinister for a further few days.JOn
OL,12,FTuesday 19 March, he will take his
OL,13,Flast First Minister's Questions which
OL,14,Fbegins at 1.30pm.JSoon after finishing
OL,15,Fthat session, he will tender his
OL,16,Fresignation to the King and once that
OL,17,Fhappens, the Senedd has 28 days to
OL,18,Fnominate another member of the Welsh
OL,19,FParliament to become First Minister.
OL,20,FIn fact, that should take place the
OL,21,Fnext day: Wednesday 20th March.
